    "As a result, the research outcomes align robustly with the definitions and forecasts of IDC.",
    "The semester, which lasted from September 2022 to December 2022, spanned 16 weeks.",
    "A total of 210 students participated in both pre-and post-tests, which assessed their listening and speaking proficiencies through online tests and interviews.",
    "Following the posttest and semi-structured interviews, the collected data underwent a statistical analysis using independent t-tests, paired sample t-test, and ANCOVA for the English proficiency test.",
